snippet.title: Andromeda Conquest gameplay (PC Game, 1982)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Andromeda Conquest, Dos PC game produced by Avalon Hill in 1982 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/andromeda-conquest/6173/
Playing a couple turns of this complex old-school science fiction strategy game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
